<major-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-07-07.0.mh" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa0707.htm">Written Answers Tuesday 7 July 2009</major-heading>

<major-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-07-07.1.mh" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa0707.htm">Scottish Executive</major-heading>

<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-07-07.S3W-25135.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa0707.htm#1">Fuel Poverty</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-07-07.S3W-25135.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80338" speakername="Johann Lamont (Glasgow Pollok) (Lab)" spid="S3W-25135" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa0707.htm#1">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive when the Scottish Fuel Poverty Forum&rsquo;s Equalities Working Group will first meet.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-07-07.S3W-25135.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80370" speakername="Alex Neil" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa0707.htm#1">

  <p>: The Scottish Fuel Poverty Forum&rsquo;s Equalities Working Group held its first meeting on 23 June.</p>

</reply>


<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-07-07.S3W-25136.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa0707.htm#1">Fuel Poverty</minor-heading>

<ques id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-07-07.S3W-25136.q0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80338" speakername="Johann Lamont (Glasgow Pollok) (Lab)" spid="S3W-25136" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa0707.htm#1">

  <p>To ask the Scottish Executive whether the minutes of the Scottish Fuel Poverty Forum&rsquo;s Equalities Working Group will be made public.</p>

</ques>


<reply id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-07-07.S3W-25136.r0" speakerid="uk.org.publicwhip/member/80370" speakername="Alex Neil" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa0707.htm#1">

  <p>Minutes of the forum meetings are published on the Scottish Government website and these will, from July, include a report back from the newly formed Fuel Poverty Forum&rsquo;s Equalities Working Group. My officials provide the secretariat for the main Scottish Fuel Poverty Forum, but not for its subgroups or working groups.</p>

</reply>


<minor-heading id="uk.org.publicwhip/spwa/2009-07-07.S3W-24932.h" nospeaker="True" url="http://www.scottish.parliament.uk/business/pqa/wa-09/wa0707.htm#2">Housing</minor-heading>

